snippet.title: How To Mechatronics
snippet.description:
Official YouTube channel of HowToMechatronics.com, an educational website in the area of Mechatronics.

Arduino Projects and Tutorials, DIY Projects, How It Works, Electronics, Robotics, CNC, 3D Printers, Tips & Tricks, Arduino Source Codes, Circuit Schematics, Download files and much more can be found at www.HowToMechatronics.com
